Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
This administration is putting the American Dream out of reach for many by targeting DACA recipients, asylum seekers, and other immigrants with exorbitant fees. This is wrong‚Äîimmigrants make our nation stronger.

My colleagues and I are fighting back.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
Laws are in place to protect whistleblowers because getting to the truth is critical to the pursuit of justice.

By potentially revealing a whistleblower‚Äôs identity, Trump is intimidating witnesses and has betrayed the public‚Äôs trust. https://t.co/VdQ1MkrgAx

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Trump is gutting the asylum process in America‚Äîsomething that is at the core of who we are as a country. Turning our backs on those lawfully seeking asylum and forcing them to ‚ÄòRemain in Mexico‚Äô is cruel, dangerous, and un-American. This has to stop. https://t.co/omoiaD0Y77

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Deeply saddened to hear of the attack in Monsey and keeping those injured in my thoughts. This was yet another vile act of anti-Semitism and it has no place in America. We must speak out and condemn this hatred whenever and wherever we see it.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: This is wrong. We know that purging voter registrations disproportionately affects people of color. This is voter suppression in plain sight. We have to fight this with everything we‚Äôve got. https://t.co/bWtwekBpAv

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Americans want law enforcement to protect and respect them, yet too many people of color continue to be targeted. Ignoring this reality is completely irresponsible. We need stronger police oversight to prevent abuses, and that must include bias training. https://t.co/KXAgiG3O5L

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
It‚Äôs clear that Mitch McConnell doesn‚Äôt want a Senate trial-he wants a Senate cover up. But he cannot undermine this process on his own.

Every one of my Senate colleagues has an obligation to pursue the truth, regardless of politics. https://t.co/DoRzhtM0XA

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: We must speak truth that there is a homelessness crisis in America, including in CA. This is an emergency that must be addressed with bold action. Congress must pass my bill with @RepMaxineWaters to invest $13 billion to eradicate chronic homelessness. https://t.co/mXVdPk3iTJ

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: A very happy #Kwanzaa to all who are celebrating in California and across the country! May your life be filled with community and joy.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: This Christmas, I‚Äôm thinking about all of our brave service members and their families in California and across the country. You make our nation proud and we are grateful for your sacrifices.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Merry Christmas! Wishing everyone who celebrates a day filled with family, friends, and good cheer.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
Our DREAMers shouldn‚Äôt live in fear of being torn from their communities, let alone during the holidays.

To our DREAMer community: I see you, and I will fight for your right to stay in the only country you know as home. https://t.co/ljMBVSrG1H

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Natalia was attacked for no other reason than the color of her skin. Her attacker must be held accountable for this. https://t.co/mwUZpKjrA1

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
Here‚Äôs something that didn‚Äôt change this decade: the federal minimum wage. Since 2009, the federal minimum wage has been $7.25 an hour. That‚Äôs not nearly enough.
 
The Senate must pass the Raise the Wage Act‚Äîwe need a $15 federal minimum wage.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: This is horrifying. Trump is turning his back on those lawfully seeking asylum in America and these are the consequences. The Trump administration must be held accountable for the inhumane ‚Äòremain in Mexico‚Äô policy. This must end. https://t.co/Xl7O0o00Rm

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Chag Sameach to all those celebrating Hanukkah! May your holiday be filled with light, love and laughter.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
Under Stephen Miller's plan, immigrant families would be forced to choose between taking over care of their children in US custody or endangering themselves.

This isn't national security‚Äîit‚Äôs white supremacy. Miller must be removed from the White House immediately. https://t.co/FGW5FsuFBj

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Transgender people‚Äîand in particular, Black trans women‚Äîare facing an epidemic of violence. We must recommit ourselves to speaking this truth and fighting anti-trans violence. My heart goes out to Yahira's family and loved ones. https://t.co/HS7dG8PqeY

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Reminder that in July, Senate Republicans sent a letter to Secretary Mnuchin demanding *even more tax cuts* for the wealthiest among us. https://t.co/DI5vg39Zh0

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Americans living in federally assisted housing do not deserve fewer privacy protections. I joined a letter with @RonWyden demanding answers on HUD's use of facial recognition technology in federally assisted housing. https://t.co/Ptybp5VlsX

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: It‚Äôs clear that John Bolton has a lot to share about Trump‚Äôs scheme to extort Ukraine. The American people deserve to know the truth‚ÄîCongress should hear from Bolton during Trump‚Äôs impeachment trial. https://t.co/86b3xwndaC

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Aretha‚Äôs songs were the soundtrack of my childhood. I was honored to lead an effort in Congress to recognize her legacy with a Congressional Gold Medal. And I‚Äôm thrilled she‚Äôll be remembered on the big screen‚Äîcan‚Äôt wait to see. https://t.co/m2FXKQj96t

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Suicide rates among children of color have increased at an alarming rate. I thank @RepBonnie and @TheBlackCaucus for bringing attention to this issue and putting forth legislation that will save lives. https://t.co/ippAYU5sR0

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: It‚Äôs wrong for any foreign government to tell Congress what members are allowed in meetings on Capitol Hill. I stand with @RepJayapal, and I'm glad her colleagues in the House did too. https://t.co/PpbDoB0zKB

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
The 5th Circuit has put the ACA one step closer to being overturned. 130 million Americans with pre-existing conditions are closer to losing their protections because Trump and Republicans care more about scoring a political win.

But this isn't the end‚Äîwe must keep fighting. https://t.co/h0zQUhWLld

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: If we want to ensure more women enter and excel in STEM careers, then we need to fundamentally change the workplace climate in these fields. My bill to combat sexual harassment in STEM passed the House months ago‚Äîthe Senate must do its job & pass my bill. https://t.co/ezv4aBpdVh

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
McConnell seems more interested in covering up Trump's misconduct than pursuing truth and fairness.

That's why it's incumbent on my colleagues to show the country there are not two sets of rules‚Äîone for Trump and another for everybody else. Read my op-ed. https://t.co/YBEQqJleCD

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
I thank the House for conducting an investigation that lived up to our founders‚Äô expectations.

It will soon fall on the Senate to fulfill its constitutional duty. I will pursue truth, fairness, and justice. I urge each of my colleagues to do the same.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
In America, nobody is above the law. And nobody, especially a president, should escape accountability.

Today, Donald J. Trump goes down as only the third president in American history to be impeached.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
It's absurd PG&E execs were awarded millions in bonuses for 'safety goals' while they put profits over safety. Lives were lost because of their negligence.

This is why I introduced a bill to ensure utility execs don't get bonuses during bankruptcy. https://t.co/LBPIiydNqH

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content:
Let‚Äôs be clear: McConnell doesn‚Äôt want a Senate trial. He wants a Senate cover up.

Every senator has a duty to use their voice and vote for a fair trial rooted in the pursuit of truth. I‚Äôll be fighting for justice‚Äîmy colleagues should too. Read my op-ed. https://t.co/YBEQqJleCD

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: It is important to remember that today's historic vote in the House is born out of patriotism and love of country. It is about having the courage to speak truth and pursue justice.

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: I can only imagine how thrilled Harvey Milk would be to witness the construction of this ship. His legacy of fighting for civil rights will live on for generations. We must continue to live by his example. https://t.co/D5rT2LoL66

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris
Content: Hundreds of thousands of voters are set to be purged from voter rolls in Wisconsin and Georgia. This is a shameful attempt at voter suppression by GOP lawmakers to rig the system in their favor. We have to fight this. https://t.co/PvaMx16dIw

Name: Vice President Kamala Harris

Name: Ibram X. Kendi
Content: For them, the #1619Project is indicative of the intellectual debate at hand over the narrative of America‚Äôs racial past, a debate they are increasingly losing. But I do not think we should just debate in print, or on social media. I think we should debate in person. 9/

Name: Ibram X. Kendi
Content: Akin to the incredibly accessible #1619Project, we‚Äôve gone with our revisionist history straight to the American people as the masters have privately seethed at our advances over the years, as they have not been able to stop our revising of America‚Äôs racial history. 8/

Name: Ibram X. Kendi
Content: The master narrative historians have blocked us when they could inside the academy, but we‚Äôve also increasingly bypassed them and landed outside of the academy in places they can‚Äôt control: from op-ed pages to trade presses to public lecture forums. 7/

Name: Ibram X. Kendi
Content: Personally, I feel eternally grateful for the pathways, institutionally and conceptually, built by the generations of revisionist historians who came before me, especially those historians who are retiring these days with battle scars and lasting legacies. 6/

Name: Ibram X. Kendi
Content: They ‚Äúblindly‚Äù critique us when reviewing our essays for history journals, our books for university presses, our records for tenure and promotion, our applications for fellowships, and our books for awards. 5/

Name: Ibram X. Kendi
Content: Instead, their critiques are made behind closed doors‚Äîoften without us knowing‚Äîas these master narrative historians try to limit our access to graduate history programs and tenure-track history jobs. 4/

Name: Ibram X. Kendi
Content: Their critiques of revisionist historians do not often hit the mainstream light, perhaps because revisionist history does not often hit the mainstream light as it did beautifully in the #1619Project. 3/

Name: Ibram X. Kendi
Content: This revisionist history has largely been written by women, by historians of color, by younger historians, by antiracist white historians. We have rejected the master narrative that has in fact been the master‚Äôs narrative. 2/
